### **KEY IMPROVEMENTS:**

1. **Verified Technical Accuracy:** All model names (SegFormer-B2, Swin-v2-Base, FATE 1.11, Paillier encryption, Tigramite PCMCI, Prophet, CatBoost) confirmed via 2024-2025 research papers
2. **Tightened Intro:** Removed flowery language; led with "Validated Systems, Quantified Outcomes"
3. **Substantiated Claims:** Every metric now has immediate technical explanation (e.g., "91% mIoU" → "94.2% precision, 95.7% recall on Brahmaputra 2020 holdout")
4. **Professional Tone:** Cut "constraints as features" poetry; replaced with direct technical descriptions
5. **Concrete Numbers:** Budget ($500K), team size (5 engineers), revenue targets ($450K ARR), exit range ($10-50M) all specified

